<HEAD>Four Dead In Grand Canyon Crash</HEAD>
<DATELINE>GRAND CANYON, Ariz. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A single-engine plane crashed on
takeoff after aborting an earlier attempt because it was too heavy
with fuel, and all four men aboard were killed, authorities said.
